title: Queens of the Stone Age - Villains (Volume Fixed)
description: There was a volume spike followed by a severe drop in level at 4:19 in "Un-Reborn Again", and the level of multiple tracks after it were inconsistent. Cover art swapped with the image from the indie version of the vinyl too, because let's be honest -- it's way the fuck cooler. Anyway, mp3s suck. Pre-order the wax below or buy it at an indie record shop with the better artwork when this thing drops on 8/25: http://store.matadorrecords.com/villains
